Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.34,0:00:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.17,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.21,0:00:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.38,0:00:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.35,0:00:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.32,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.40,0:01:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.13,0:01:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.90,0:01:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.21,0:01:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船和義體用浮力背包已經放到這個地址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.96,0:01:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，你拿這麼點武器想幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.23,0:01:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去支持難民解放啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.77,0:01:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙也夠辛苦的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我只要能賺得到錢就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.12,0:02:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，這是什麼玩意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全按計劃進行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.51,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙出賣我們，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#07 狂想乃亡國之曲調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊總理，擁有高規格義體的男子身份查證得如何了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然以軍方相關人員為中心清查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但目前沒有符合條件的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援直升機失控事件發生之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍方的防護就變得異常嚴密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且那個高規格的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去在自衛軍的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只記載了以PKF名義派遣的部隊曾換裝過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.24,0:03:34.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,PKF：Peace Keeping Forces 聯合國維和部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道什麼原因非但沒有PKF的名冊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.08,0:03:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連作戰記錄都消失得乾乾淨淨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,免維修保養的PKF型號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.95,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在新宿核電廠案中有所行動的那個組織呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊也沒有具體進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新內閣上台後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嶄露頭角的新官方機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.53,0:04:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且跟自衛軍關係良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.87,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,11架失控的直升機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彷彿跟這件事呼應一般開始現身的「個別的11人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.38,0:04:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一直隱藏在新宿地底深處的核能發電設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然手裏的問題堆積如山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為了核電廠挖出來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長那傢伙不是又被叫到首相那邊去了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，有什麼不滿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你不覺得奇怪嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得9課應該是個攻擊性的組織吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣被掐著脖子做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不就連一個先發制人的機會都沒有了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不否認你說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，課長大概也是這麼想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.58,0:04:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此，那為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為對9課來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最大的敵人是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.65,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然問這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且在壓倒性的人、物力資源面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.30,0:05:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這種組織根本無計可施只有失敗一途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果現在這個狀況本身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是對我們的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不難想像有可能在某處有什麼東西正在蠢蠢欲動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在新宿地底深處的核電廠回填作業當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回收了鈽燃料棒的事情你應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.69,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大致情況有聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我們一直在進行秘密運送那些燃料棒的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這個情報在計劃實施前被人洩漏給了恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.97,0:05:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對政府在等待被解放為新國民的難民腳下所做的愚行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們欲加之以天譴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.02,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以難民的手在難民的土地上挖出的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.29,0:06:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們認為歸還給難民較為妥當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面也有那個標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到那個聲明之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海上保安廳雖然成功破獲了武器交易現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.24,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，數量驚人的槍械很有可能已經完成交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.61,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當初的運送計劃考慮使用海路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是從恐怖份子遺留的收據上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們預估在海上會遭到襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此緊急變更計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.46,0:06:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說希望由9課負責陸路運送嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.30,0:06:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們對外並不存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最適合負責運送這些原本不該存在的戰前遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理您對這件事怎麼看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得是...很適當的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.76,0:07:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以問您一件事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.50,0:07:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您對新宿核電廠的存在知道多少呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.67,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到發現鈽的消息時才第一次知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下告退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰內容就像事前說明的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.52,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將那個核電廠挖出來的鈽經由陸路運出難民居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那果然是政府主導的秘密挖掘計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明知如此為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9課從哪時候開始改行當總理的手下了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們並沒有改行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那為何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.74,0:08:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只是被某人搶先下手罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧，課長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.16,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的第一次空降作戰有諸位同行真是讓我感到非常放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙為什麼出現在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還說要跟我們同行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過是處理無聊的戰爭遺物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.31,0:08:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛要我一起去啊真是氣死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次謝謝你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內閣情報廳戰略影響調查會議代表輔佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.95,0:08:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-抱歉把討厭的工作推給你們\N-合田一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.11,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎接的部隊按預定計劃從新濱出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.19,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是能繼續這樣不出意外就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.59,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像動物園的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說這種會引起反感的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爬過鐵絲網的話不是被射殺就是驅逐出境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.55,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們也知道後果的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.96,0:10:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地的自衛軍連自己在保護什麼都沒有被告知嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.50,0:10:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這世上有很多事情還是不知道比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了在事後能夠迅速操作情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.41,0:10:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也希望知道真相的人能夠維持在最少限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.08,0:10:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.81,0:10:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次全部作戰都交給你們內廳做如何?反正...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.32,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然第一次見到你 不過，最近好像在哪裏...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤、帕茲、波瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在當地調到卡車之後 22:00前跟我們會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把塔奇克馬也帶去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.91,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次希望你們不要使用思考戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想刺激難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我瞭解作戰的所有權限在你手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在現場希望你服從我們的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我不保證你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，請你跟他做雙人跳傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們也下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最怕這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要拖拖拉拉的，走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.79,0:12:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到通知說這玩意是鈽之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是冷汗流個不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.83,0:12:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來就由我們運出難民居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我的部下也有可能已經遭受輻射傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.74,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的，不用擔心那種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿西裝的懂什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對穿西裝的感到失望是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，這是政府的方針
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.11,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各部門有自己既定的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想做的話可以脫下制服離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這樣你們大概還是會憤憤不平吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我有件事要拜託你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用有線的方式談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 不要在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擦屁股是穿西裝的人的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車輛到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們出一名副官和兩名步哨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是讓步方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.52,0:13:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，車輛補給完畢之後就出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得心裏毛毛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.01,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然無法否定個別的11人計劃搶奪鈽的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們並沒有跟難民合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能保持警戒雖然再好不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，別疑心生暗鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比起這個我更在意海上運送的情報是從哪裏洩漏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是知道這輛車上面有鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些難民應該會很吃驚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少在那裏廢話連篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.60,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你們不同 說話可是我的專長啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真無邪的小鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你們知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在長崎的難民居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.15,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛發生那個年紀的少女對警察開槍的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你讓同伴感到不安幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的隊員似乎受過嚴格訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個女隊長看起來更是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.34,0:16:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來你為什麼加入她這一隊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.81,0:16:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會是迷上她了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿口胡說八道的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川，路線查得怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳送從衛星得到的情報給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成高架道路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會危險嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走到舊高速公路就已經脫離難民居住區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再來把貨物交給從橫須賀基地來接收的人任務就結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比較危險的反而是環狀道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.48,0:16:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分的大樓都倒塌荒廢把道路兩旁都塞住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果恐怖份子埋伏在那裏我們根本就擋不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.75,0:17:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真了不起的作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.05,0:17:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田那傢伙到底在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川，路線清查一遍之後去查查他的底細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.19,0:17:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正打算這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大戰之後30年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在還把關東這樣丟著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.25,0:17:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歸根究底還是難民問題持續不了了之所造成的爛帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.25,0:17:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許已經快到臨界點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.53,0:17:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從我這邊也看得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有種不好的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川，你看得見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以，是翻車事故嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去查看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.89,0:18:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,考量安全問題的話，應該繞路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且考量到我們運送的貨物內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.66,0:18:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更應該盡可能避免陷入戰鬥狀態才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.57,0:18:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是為此才改穿本地的迷彩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先派出斥候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.14,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，那裏面要是藏有恐怖份子只有橫下心來衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼人選是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和齋藤過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給巴特指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看我長這樣還挺受難民歡迎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上一個陸自的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的部下殺氣太重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就如你看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是西區的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們急著趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思沒空幫你們的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我們先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.65,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨你高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.19,0:19:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡車旁邊的寬度夠車輛通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢靠近，如果情況不對馬上丟下我們衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.73,0:19:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援軍嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，那傢伙有槍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩，衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.99,0:20:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.30,0:20:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.87,0:20:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有異狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是普通的難民嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了無謂的殺生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝恐怖份子的情報看來是唬人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好只是白費了些力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次9課也做得非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是在挖苦我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是真心誠意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.65,0:22:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.65,0:22:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.42,0:22:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.16,0:22:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔營完畢的陸自第二臨時小隊現在應該已經把鈽送到海上了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.03,0:22:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你拿我們當誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.33,0:22:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我們當成什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.03,0:22:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們才是把自己當成什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,篩選出來的少數精銳部隊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.67,0:22:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要用一流槍械武裝的難民們大舉進攻的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們根本無計可施不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.85,0:22:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我導演之下能演個誘餌角色你們就應該偷笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.72,0:23:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.46,0:23:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.97,0:23:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.20,0:23:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.71,0:23:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字——然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.45,0:23:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我——時間已經到了
